OL,6,FA man has admitted to stabbing his
OL,7,Fwife to death at their home in Bilston
OL,8,Fin December.
OL,10,FRajveer Mahey was charged with the
OL,11,Fmurder of 46-year-old Kamaljeet Mahey
OL,12,Fon Park Meadow Avenue in December last
OL,13,Fyear.JThe 50-year-old pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto her murder at Wolverhampton Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Monday 18 March.
OL,17,FRajveer Mahey is being remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody for sentencing on 19 April.
